  • Method Details

    • logExchange

      void logExchange(GTNet gtNet, GTNetExchangeKindType entityKind, boolean asSupplier, int entitiesSent, int entitiesUpdated, int entitiesInResponse)
      Logs an exchange operation. Creates an INDIVIDUAL period log entry.
      Parameters:
      gtNet - the remote GTNet domain
      entityKind - the type of data exchanged
      asSupplier - true if logging as supplier, false if as consumer
      entitiesSent - number of entities sent or received
      entitiesUpdated - number of entities successfully updated
      entitiesInResponse - number of entities in the response

    • aggregateLogs

      int aggregateLogs(GTNetExchangeLogPeriodType fromPeriod, GTNetExchangeLogPeriodType toPeriod, LocalDate beforeDate)
      Aggregates log entries from one period type to the next. Groups entries by (idGtNet, entityKind, logAsSupplier) and sums statistics.
      Parameters:
      fromPeriod - the source period type to aggregate from
      toPeriod - the target period type to aggregate to
      beforeDate - only aggregate entries with periodStart before this date
      Returns:
      number of source entries that were aggregated

    • getExchangeLogTree

      GTNetExchangeLogTreeDTO getExchangeLogTree(Integer idGtNet, GTNetExchangeKindType entityKind)
      Gets the exchange log tree structure for a specific GTNet and entity kind. Returns hierarchical data with supplier and consumer totals.
      Parameters:
      idGtNet - the GTNet identifier
      entityKind - the entity kind to filter by
      Returns:
      tree structure DTO for frontend display

    • getAllExchangeLogTrees

      List<GTNetExchangeLogTreeDTO> getAllExchangeLogTrees(GTNetExchangeKindType entityKind)
      Gets all log entries for all GTNets that support communication for the specified entity kind. Only returns GTNets where the corresponding GTNetEntity has exchange enabled.
      Parameters:
      entityKind - the entity kind to filter by
      Returns:
      list of tree DTOs, one per GTNet with communication enabled for this entity kind
